OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly mist, patchy fog or low
OL,6,Fcloud disperses. Then bright with
OL,7,Foften large amounts of high cloud, and
OL,8,Fa chance of showers. Slightly warmer
OL,9,Ffor many areas than on Saturday.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudy at times, with some
OL,12,Fisolated showers at first. Where
OL,13,Fbreaks develop we could see some fog
OL,14,Fpatches forming before dawn. Winds
OL,15,Fgenerally light but breezy along the
OL,16,Fcoast.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FSome occasional bright spells
OL,19,Fand scattered heavy showers developing
OL,20,Fduring the afternoon. Temperatures
OL,21,Fslightly cooler than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
