OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FTuesday cloudy with heavy showers.
OL,7,FWednesday and Thursday, dry with
OL,8,Fbright or sunny spells. Temperatures
OL,9,Fgenerally near average inland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
